text: Metta is a given name. Notable people with the name include: *Metta Fock (1765–1810), Swedish noble and sentenced murderer *Metta Permadi (born 1989), Indonesian actress *Metta Spencer (born 1931), Canadian sociologist *Metta von Oberg (1737–1794), German baroness *Metta World Peace (born 1979), American basketball coach and former player ==See also== *Meta (name), given name and surname
